computation_code.description:
Python code defining compute_measurement(time, species_dict, ureg). Converts model species to observable matching calibration target. Must return Pint Quantity for comparison. Example:
def compute_measurement(time, species_dict, ureg):
    cd8 = species_dict['V_T.CD8']
    tumor = species_dict['V_T.C1']
    ratio = cd8 / tumor
    return ratio.to(ureg.dimensionless)

